C400 [*] Unnecessary generator (rewrite as a list comprehension)
 --> C400_py315.py:3:1
  |
1 | xs = [[1], [2]]
2 |
3 | list(*x for x in xs)
  | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
  |
help: Rewrite as a list comprehension
1 | xs = [[1], [2]]
2 |
  - list(*x for x in xs)
3 + [*x for x in xs]
note: This is an unsafe fix and may change runtime behavior
